If you are a mice living inside of the laboratory. Your innate fear resources come from: fox urine, cat fur, rat bedding, snake skin, looming shadow, approaching tone.

Please try this for a moment.

如果你是住在实验室内的老鼠。 你天生的恐惧资源来自：狐狸尿，猫皮，老鼠寝具，蛇皮，逼真的阴影，逼近的色调。

请尝试一下。

